description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'FAT BURNING Beginner Stationary Bike Workout | 20 Minute' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Cycling.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Groove Session vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This 20 minute stationary bike workout for beginners is great for burning fat and losing weight!
